_sText: ZM_UNPANIC BY UNREAL ORIGINAL VERSION BY LILA Here is my first zombie-mod map. This is a 100% remade version of Lilas map, you will notice its VERY diferent, but still has similar structure. Includes over 30 diferent spots, its balanced, and very well optimized for better FPS performance. Made for FRAGXLs ZM 64 slots server, I hope you people like it, have fun.
